===Etymology===
A loanword taken from the Malay language with compounding, addition of the word “sama”. In the Malay language, “sama” which means, “the same” and “sama-sama” in Malay means “together”.

====Usage====
Commonly used in spoken Singapore Colloquial English, found mostly in blogs, blogs, but only in recent years (2006- 2015).